The paper deals with the task of Relation Extraction (RE) which is a subfield of Natural Language Processing (NLP) and falls under the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also uses Knowledge Bases (KBs) and KB Embeddings (KBE) which are related to Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of heterogeneous representations which can be related to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Databases (cs.DB).
